      java.lang.String toString()
      Construct the textual representation of the DFA, for example A simple two state DFA Q = { a b } Sigma = { 0 1 } delta = 0 1 a a b b a b q0 = a F = { b } The order of the states and the alphabet is the order in which they were instantiated in the DFA.
